  "body": "\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nIf you've experienced a bug, please provide the following information:\r\n\r\n### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nWhen you access your wallet with MetaMask as you normally would, everything is okay, until you manually sign out of the MetaMask extension. On MyCrypto, it still shows that you are logged int and can still proceed to send a transaction. MyCrypto should also \"log out\" of the wallet.  \r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Access with MetaMask\r\n2. Log out of MetaMask extenstion\r\n\r\n### Description of Your Machine\r\n\r\nChrome, Windows 10\r\n\r\n### Console Logs / Screenshots\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25834495/39888091-d9de958a-5461-11e8-9135-fc75c862cb15.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25834495/39888114-e954f0a4-5461-11e8-8022-35825a8d1197.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
